data.description: Beautifully quiet neighborhood, remodeled house to raise a family. Just a few blocks to all the bars, restaurants, and retail at Hollywood Blvd. Currently rented by a tenant for $ 5,000 a month, the lease will expire in March 2024. Covered patio & built-in BBQ area, impact windows, mango tree, Circular driveway & one car garage. It is in the heart of Hollywood close to shopping, restaurants & an easy commute to 95 or the Turnpike, close to Seminole Hard Rock Casino,  Aventura Mall, Hard Work Stadium, Close to Fort Lauderdale Airport, Miami Airport, close to Regional Memorial Hospital.
